  <brief_title>Evaluation of Preoperative Investigations in Patients With Liver Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Positron Emission Tomography/ CT Scan, Endoscopic Ultrasono¬Graphy, and Laparoscopic Ultrasonography in the Preoperative Assess¬Ment of Resectability in Patients With Primary and Secondary Liver Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
